## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="bc0c1-126">В следующем примере отображается каждая <xref:System.Data.OleDb.OleDbError> в <xref:System.Data.OleDb.OleDbErrorCollection> коллекции.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="bc0c1-126">The following example displays each <xref:System.Data.OleDb.OleDbError> within the <xref:System.Data.OleDb.OleDbErrorCollection> collection.</span></span>  

```csharp  
public void DisplayOleDbErrorCollection(OleDbException myException)   
  {  
     for (int i=0; i < myException.Errors.Count; i++)  
     {  
        MessageBox.Show("Index #" + i + "\n" +  
               "Message: " + myException.Errors[i].Message + "\n" +  
               "Native: " + myException.Errors[i].NativeError.ToString() + "\n" +  
               "Source: " + myException.Errors[i].Source + "\n" +  
               "SQL: " + myException.Errors[i].SQLState + "\n");  
     }  
  }  
```
